Interface UploadProgressListener

    The listener interface for receiving upload progress events.
    用于接收上载进度事件的侦听器界面。

    • Method Detail

      • onProgressChanged

        void onProgressChanged(int uploadPositionInBytes,
                       int uploadSizeInBytes)
        Invoked when upload progress has been updated. Please note, that progress events are fired only in case file upload takes some time, for small files this event may not fired. Also, there is no guarantee that this method will be invoked when upload has been completed. When upload has been completed the engine loads a new web page, so in order to find out when upload has been completed, listen to the
        更新上传进度时调用。请注意，仅在文件上传需要花费一些时间的情况下才会触发进度事件，对于小文件，此事件可能不会触发。同样，不能保证上传完成后将调用此方法。上传完成后，引擎会加载新的网页，因此，要找出上传完成的时间，请收听
        Parameters:
        uploadPositionInBytes - - a number of the bytes uploaded --上传的字节数
        uploadSizeInBytes - - a total number of bytes that should be uploaded --应该上传的总字节数
